##

<span key="67eb21687cf4485582e92cbbd4afd1aa"><span offset-key="67eb21687cf4485582e92cbbd4afd1aa:0">Each product will have a single registered domain that will be used for all endpoints in all services and for all projects.</span></span>

    <span key="de7ecd4795a448699bd8bace4150f418"><span offset-key="de7ecd4795a448699bd8bace4150f418:0">Domain name registration for products will be handled by Labs Engineering Managers</span></span>

    <span key="5a1fd61246594ed6abcf10baaaaf1e73"><span offset-key="5a1fd61246594ed6abcf10baaaaf1e73:0">Nameservers will be provided by an AWS Route 53 Hosted Zone</span></span>

    <span key="5424b6c3fae745ee9d56c92cebe1e604"><span offset-key="5424b6c3fae745ee9d56c92cebe1e604:0">Naming Standard</span></span>

        <span key="9985ef6faed64b418cc1a4e40b6f5868"><span offset-key="9985ef6faed64b418cc1a4e40b6f5868:0">Use the </span>`dev`<span offset-key="9985ef6faed64b418cc1a4e40b6f5868:2"> TLD only</span></span>
